    "BattleFrontier_BattleArenaLobby_Text_OrderOfMonsImportant": "In the BATTLE ARENA, the order of\\nPOKéMON is totally important.\\pFor example, if your first POKéMON\\nhas certain type disadvantages,\\ltry making your second POKéMON one\\lwith moves that are super effective\\lagainst the first one.\\pI think that will be a good way of\\nmaking an effective team.",
